Class RectangleConstraintSolver

      spatial.rectangleAlgebra.RectangleConstraintSolver

Direct Known Subclasses:
AugmentedRectangleConstraintSolver
public class RectangleConstraintSolver
extends ConstraintSolver

This class represents Rectangle constraints. Each constraint represents two dimension Allen relations between spatial entities. In rectangle Algebra, each spatial entity is restricted to be an axes parallel rectangle.

Author:
Iran Mansouri
